I am trying to upload a file to a servlet.

The servlet gets the name of the file as the parameter value for the appropriate
parameter, but the actual file (which I expected to read with request.getReader,
or request.getInputStream) comes back empty (the StringBuffer in the example
code below).

            BufferedReader reader = req.getReader();
            if( reader != null )
            {
                StringBuffer sb = new StringBuffer();
                String currLine = reader.readLine();
                while( currLine != null )
                {
                    sb.append( "<BR>" );
                    sb.append( currLine );
                    currLine = reader.readLine();
                }
                data.put( "BodyOfRequest", sb.toString() );
            }
